This React application allows users to generate excuses based on different scenarios such as party, family, or office. Upon selecting a reason, the app sends a request to an API endpoint, fetching an excuse related to the chosen reason and displaying it dynamically. The UI presents buttons for each scenario, triggering the excuse generation process upon clicking. The layout is styled using CSS, featuring a centered design with rounded borders and hover effects for visual appeal. Additionally, the application ensures responsiveness by adjusting to different screen sizes. Overall, this simple yet engaging app provides a playful way for users to generate humorous excuses for various situations.
